    "en": {
      "title": "18-hour water cut in Colombo and suburbs on Saturday, Sunday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An 18-hour water cut will be in effect in Colombo and its suburbs from 8.00 a.m Saturday (September 3) till 2.00 a.m on Sunday (September 4) the National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NSWDB ) said.",
        "In a statement the NSWDB said that Colombo, Dehiwela- Mount Lavinia, Sri Jayawardenapura Kotte, Kaduwela Municipality areas, Maharagama, Boralesgamuwa, Kolonnawa Municipality areas, Kotikawatta, Mulleriyawa, Ratmalana and Katubedda will be affected."
      ],
